T1  - A Trajectory Method for the Optimization of the Multi-Facility Location Problem With lp Distances
AU  - Drezner, Z.
AU  - Wesolowsky, G. O.
Y1  - 1978/10/01
PY  - 1978
DA  - 1978/10/01
